      <div class="why-card reveal d2"><div class="why-num">02</div><h3>No Hidden Charges</h3><p>You get a clear quote before we start. No surprise fees. No pressure upsells.</p></div>
      <div class="why-card reveal d3"><div class="why-num">03</div><h3>We Come to You</h3><p>Based in Pasig, we cover all of Metro Manila. Book via WhatsApp and we schedule at your convenience.</p></div>
      <div class="why-card reveal d4"><div class="why-num">04</div><h3>All Brands Covered</h3><p>Kelvinator, Samsung, LG, Daikin, Carrier, Fujitsu, Midea — we service them all.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section id="how">
