      </div>
      <div class="step reveal-scale d3">
        <div class="step-num">Step 03</div>
        <div class="step-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>We Do the Work</h3><p>Our technician arrives on time, fully equipped. We clean, check, and test your unit — zero mess left behind.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal-scale d4">
        <div class="step-num">Step 04</div>
        <div class="step-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Enjoy Cold, Clean Air</h3><p>Your aircon runs better, cooler, and more efficiently. We follow up to make sure you're satisfied.</p>
